{
  "stem": "5516.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They had already subways, and they had buses, you know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You used to go each 5-10 minutes, yeah.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In my town was living 35,000.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "9,000 Jews.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In public school, I didn't go because for Jewish people, it's hard to go in there.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Maybe in the whole public school maybe was two, three people.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Oh, we had-- the Jewish community had a-- a gymnasium they call this, a high school.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they had professional, beautiful teachers, you know, from Switzerland and from Germany, you know?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they supervised-- not supervised-- the Lithuanian government education--",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--department used to control this, you know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They didn't support us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But they controlled us, you know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When they-- when we had the examens, they used to come in--",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--you know, and check if everything goes right.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they had-- they used to even send out-- the controllers, they used to send out in Jerusalem to teach them the Hebrew language because everything was in Hebrew.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they would send the non-Jewish controllers to Jerusalem.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To Jerusalem in a-- in a university.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they used to graduate for the Hebrew language.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And after this, they used to come in.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They used to control the, the--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--Jewish gymnasium.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, I remember bar mitzvah, yeah.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The bar--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The bar mitzvah-- beside, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] beside in, in the gymnasium, they teach us religion, you know, the Bible, and the Tanakh, and all kind stuff.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When-- on the end, after school, my father used to send me to a, a rabbi, a private rabbi, for teaching, you know, this Judaic study.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And before bar mitzvah, they had a student-- we used to go to became a, a rabbi.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They had special places where people go to became rabbis.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it's not like in United States, four years.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
